Key Match Events: Travis Head was named Player of the Match with scores of 62 runs and taking 2 wickets.
David Warner scored 29 runs before being dismissed by Aiden Markram.
Steven Smith scored 30 runs before being dismissed by Gerald Coetzee.
Marnus Labuschagne scored 18 runs before being dismissed by Tabraiz Shamsi.
Glenn Maxwell scored 1 run before being dismissed by Shamsi.
Josh Inglis scored 28 runs before being dismissed by Coetzee.
Pat Cummins remained not out on 14 runs.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at Eden Gardens, Kolkata.
South Africa won the toss and elected to bat first.
The match was a day-night 50-over match.
Travis Head was named the Man of the Match.
Others: The match was part of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023-24 and Australia advanced in the series.
